        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Ancestors of the Rittenhouse family were paper-makers, and William Rittenhouse built the first papermill in America in 1690 on the Wissahickon Creek in Roxborough (Pa.). William's grandson, David Rittenhouse, was a famous astronomer.</p>
